Change deployment roles

Get the deployment role ARNs from environment secrets.

Configure OpenTelemetry collector

Refactor deployment to support emitting metrics to an OLTP endpoint directly, rather than to a local collector in a layer.

Fix deployment (#1613)

Fix configuration by building the command line with an array so `--layers` can have a conditional value.

Use AWS Secrets Manager

Use AWS Secrets Manager to store the 4 secrets the application uses, rather than rely on GitHub Actions secrets.

Fix missing telemetry

Fix missing telemetry due to `OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT` no longer being set in the environment variables.

Fix configuration

- Fix configuration being registered as `IConfiguratonRoot`, which meant it didn't override the default `IConfiguration`, so was missing the AWS Secret Manager-provided values.
- Update test to add coverage for issue.
